      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like everything is getting so heavy lately. my joints ache every single morning and i can see how tired my daughter looks every time she comes over to help me with the laundry or the dishes. i hate seeing that look in her eyes... like she's just counting down the minutes until she can leave. i feel like i'm just taking up space and making everyone's lives harder.",
